(1405, 154, 'wpcf-action-description-in-english', 'The action supports strengthening the human potential in higher education and research to improve the quality and efficiency of higher education by facilitating their active participation in contemporary research projects for the enrichment of the research work.\r\n\r\nIts main objective is the acquisition and development of a research culture and the promotion of scientific knowledge to young researchers. At the same time, it aims at enhancing the mobility of researchers so that new knowledge produced by research can be disseminated through education, resulting in well-trained people able to apply new technological and organizational methods.'),
