(1303, 170, 'wpcf-action-description-in-english', 'The strategic objective is to promote experimental solutions to address social challenges through new forms of open partnership co-operation, new technologies and new business models. Social challenges are reflected in National Priorities of Oriented Research, Experimental Development and Innovation up to 2030, i.e.: Competitive knowledge-based economy, Sustainability of the energy sector and material resources, Environment for quality life, Social and cultural challenges, Healthy population, Safe society.'),
