(1011, 192, 'wpcf-action-description-in-english', 'This action supports grant programs for the improvement of existing facilities for R&D entities. More specifically, innovation companies, clusters, technology platforms, public applicants (municipalities, regions, etc.), research organisations and other R&D institutions can apply for a grant.'),
