(333, 23, '2018-06-20 14:02:29', '2018-06-20 11:02:29', 'The Region of Epirus has launched a strategic marketing plan to extend the tourism season and give Epirus the title of the “ideal destination for all four seasons.” Epirus occupies the northwest corner of the Greek peninsula and is the most mountainous region in Greece. The largest city in Epirus is Ioannina.', 'RIS3 action plan Region Epirus', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ris3-action-plan-region-epirus', '', '', '2018-06-22 14:27:01', '2018-06-22 11:27:01', '', 0, 'http://actionplan.s3platform.eu/?post_type=action-plan&#038;p=333', 0, 'action-plan', '', 0),
